parameters:
\SE[17]I'm sorry, I'm late...!! \!\SE[4]I came to...
\!\SE[3]help, but...

\SE[72]You're late, aren't you? I had some free time, so I
took care of it over here.
\SE[29]Please don't do it alone! It's so wet...!!

\SE[68]Oh no... It feels like I missed my chance to be on
stage... \SE[3]...But still, we made a huge hole, didn't we?
\SE[2]This is going to be a lot of repair costs.

\SE[2]Let's cover the expenses with the Rare Earth we obtain
in this battle. \SE[7]If we do that, the land will also
expand, and we can profit from it all.

\SE[2]I wonder if they're... alright. \SE[3]I hope they're
safe.

\SE[2]It's hard to imagine Lunaroa being a hindrance...
\!\SE[3]Well, we're done here, so let's go provide support.
